snippet.title: Diana and Roma Family Fun Time at the Amusement Park
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma with their parents visited Parc Astérix in Paris and had a great time! The amusement park is beautiful and closely related to comic book stories. It has been designed for all ages, even toddlers! Ride the rides with us!
Thanks for watching!
